Class Agent

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.GECLYfinalproj.Agent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ninja, Player

    public abstract class Agent
extends java.lang.Object
implements Locatable
    This class represents an agent in the game (enemies and the player) and is the parent class for Player and Ninja.
